# INSPIROIN Portfolio — Project Knowledge

> **Maintenance:** This file is the single source of project truth. Agents must keep it updated whenever the codebase changes — see `.cursor/rules/sync-project-knowledge.mdc` (always applied; no user prompt needed).

## What This Project Is

Marketing website for **INSPIROIN** — Shopify + custom web agency (Bengaluru, India).

**Two pillars (always balance both in copy):**
1. **Shopify** — store builds, apps, themes, Plus, migrations, store management
2. **Custom websites** — fully bespoke sites with **own admin panel**, backend, portals (NOT Shopify)

**Contact:** support@inspiroin.com · Monday to Saturday, 10AM – 7PM IST · Bengaluru, Karnataka, India

**Live URL (metadata):** https://inspiroin.com

