## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|-------|--------|
| Framework | Next.js **16.2.9** (App Router) |
| UI | React **19.2.7**, TypeScript **5.5** |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS **3.4**, CSS variables in `app/globals.css` |
| Motion | Framer Motion **11.3**, GSAP **3.15** + ScrollTrigger |
| Scroll | Lenis **1.1** smooth scroll (via `SmoothScroll.tsx`) |
| Email | nodemailer **8** — Brevo SMTP for contact form |

**Fonts:** Space Grotesk (display), Inter (body), JetBrains Mono (mono) — loaded in `app/layout.tsx`.

**NOT used:** Polaris React, Shopify embedded admin UI, Tailwind-only external UI libs, Redux, Formik.

