## Global Layout (`app/layout.tsx`)

Always present:
- `#bg-layer` — fixed background canvas
- `SmoothScroll` — Lenis instance; export `getLenis()` for scroll-to-top
- `ScrollRefresh` — ScrollTrigger refresh on route change
