## Design System

**CSS tokens** (`app/globals.css`): `--bg`, `--surface`, `--accent` (#4868d1), `--heading`, tints (`--tint-lavender`, etc.)

**Dynamic tint classes:** `bg-${tint}` used in cards — **safelisted** in `tailwind.config.ts`:
`bg-tint-pink`, `bg-tint-lavender`, `bg-tint-mint`, `bg-tint-sky`

**Images:** `next/image`; remote Unsplash allowed; hero + industries use local `public/images/`

**Easing:** `--ease-signature: cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)` / `EASE` in `lib/motion.ts`

**Reduced motion:** Lenis disabled; animations simplified via `useReducedMotion()` throughout.

