## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Fix |
|-------|-----|
| `framer-motion` vendor chunk error | Delete `.next` folder, restart `npm run dev` |
| Content invisible until scroll on inner pages | `Reveal.tsx` viewport + mount check (already fixed) |
| `params` Promise error on detail pages | Next.js 16: `await params` in `/services/[slug]` and `/work/[slug]` |

